<p><b>Writer - Modern Text Processing</b></p>
<p>The application for writing letters, editing files in other formats, creating tables of contents, managing footnotes and endnotes, and using the thesaurus.</p>
<p><b>Calc - Professional Spreadsheets</b></p>
<p>Calc is an efficient tool for spreadsheets of all complexity levels. Its advanced technology supports formulas in "natural language" and features a scenario manager for "What if...?" questions.</p>
<p><b>Impress and Draw</b></p>
<p>The presentation often constitutes the most important part of your work. The complete office suite includes the presentation application Impress and the drawing application Draw. Unleash your creativity!</p>
